			<div class="content" id="post-content-4727952">
									

<p>As a general note, the Butterfly Squad is the only group of reviewers who handles critique of material before it is posted to the mainsite, and they review drafts and concepts, not just the latter.</p>
<p>Butterfly Squad is typically invitation-only, though I will take requests for consideration to join the Roster. Simply send me a PM noting you are interested in being considered&#8212;I will then respond with the criteria (generally links to recent reviews, and some statements about different aspects of the forum experience) to provide for staff to look over and determine if the reviewer should be added to the Roster.</p>

